net.xqhs.flash.core.Loader

  • Packages that use Loader 
    Package Description
    net.xqhs.flash.core
    The package contains the core of Flash-MAS.

    net.xqhs.flash.core.node

    • Uses of Loader in net.xqhs.flash.core

      Classes in net.xqhs.flash.core that implement Loader 
      Modifier and Type Class Description
      static class  Loader.SimpleLoader
      Simple implementation for Loader, which attempts to load the entity class by instantiating it: using a constructor that receives a MultiTreeMap as argument, or using the default constructor, and if the instance implements ConfigurableEntity, subsequently calling ConfigurableEntity.configure(net.xqhs.flash.core.util.MultiTreeMap).

    • Uses of Loader in net.xqhs.flash.core.composite

      Classes in net.xqhs.flash.core.composite that implement Loader 
      Modifier and Type Class Description
      class  CompositeAgentLoader
      Agent loader for agents extending CompositeAgent.

    • Uses of Loader in net.xqhs.flash.core.node

      Classes in net.xqhs.flash.core.node that implement Loader 
      Modifier and Type Class Description
      class  NodeLoader
      The NodeLoader class manages the loading of one node in the system (normally, there is one node per machine, therefore this manages booting FLASH-MAS on the current machine).
